Add user-adjustable drop delay slider to Plinko

- Added `dropDelay` state (default 400ms) replacing hardcoded BALL_SPAWN_DELAY constant
- Drop Delay control (slider + −/+ buttons) appears when ball count > 1
- Range: 50ms–2000ms in 50ms steps; live value display in seconds
- Slider/buttons disabled while dropping is in progress
- Added dropDelay to handleDrop useCallback dependency array
